<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Forfeo Lab | Excellence Client</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --primary: #00aaff; --dark: #050505; --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); }
        body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--dark); color: white; overflow-x: hidden; }

        /* Loader Scanner Futuriste */
        #loader { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: var(--dark); z-index: 9999; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: opacity 0.5s; }
        .scanner { width: 280px; height: 2px; background: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--primary); animation: scan 2.5s infinite ease-in-out; }
        @keyframes scan { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(-70px); opacity: 0.1; } 50% { transform: translateY(70px); opacity: 1; } }

        /* Navigation Style GitHub Lab */
        nav { position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; padding: 25px; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 40px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(15px); z-index: 1000; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
        nav a { color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 2px; opacity: 0.6; transition: 0.3s; text-transform: uppercase; }
        nav a:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--primary); }

        /* Hero Section Inspired by FORFEO-LAB */
        .hero { height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #111 0%, #050505 100%); padding: 0 20px; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 5.5rem; margin: 0; font-weight: 800; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff 40%, var(--primary)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .hero p { max-width: 750px; font-size: 1.3rem; opacity: 0.6; line-height: 1.6; margin: 20px 0 40px; }

        .auth-box { display: flex; gap: 25px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
        .glass-card { background: var(--glass); backdrop-filter: blur(25px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 24px; padding: 45px; width: 380px; transition: 0.4s ease; }
        .glass-card:hover { border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-8px); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }

        input { width: 100%; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 18px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); border: 1px solid #222; color: white; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 14px; outline: none; transition: 0.3s; }
        input:focus { border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,170,255,0.1); }
        
        .btn { width: 100%; padding: 18px; border: none; border-radius: 12px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: 0.3s; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: white; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 170, 255, 0.3); }
        .btn-primary:hover { filter: brightness(1.2); transform: scale(1.02); }

        /* Mission Section */
        .mission-container { padding: 120px 20px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 40px; }
        .mission-card { background: var(--glass); padding: 50px 35px; border-radius: 20px; border-top: 2px solid var(--primary); }
        .mission-card h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="loader"><div class="scanner"></div><p style="margin-top: 50px; letter-spacing: 6px; font-size: 11px; opacity: 0.5;">CHARGEMENT DU LABORATOIRE...</p></div>

    <nav>
        <a href="/">Accueil</a>
        <a href="/business-plans">Solutions Business</a>
        <a href="/candidature">Ambassadeurs</a>
        <a href="/partenaires">Partenaires</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Forfeo Lab</h1>
        <p>L'excellence client n'est plus une option. C'est une science combinant l'intelligence artificielle et l'œil critique de nos ambassadeurs certifiés.</p>

        <div class="auth-box">
            <div class="glass-card">
                <h2 style="margin-top:0;">Connexion Business</h2>
                <form action="/login-entreprise" method="POST">
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email professionnel" required>
                    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Mot de passe" required>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Accéder au Dashboard</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mission-container">
        <div class="mission-card">
            <h3>01. Audit Immersif</h3>
            <p style="opacity:0.6;">Nos ambassadeurs agissent incognito pour capturer la réalité brute de votre service.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-card">
            <h3>02. Analyse IA</h3>
            <p style="opacity:0.6;">L'IA Forfy traite les rapports pour extraire des points de friction invisibles à l'œil nu.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-card">
            <h3>03. Certification</h3>
            <p style="opacity:0.6;">Validez vos standards et obtenez le label d'excellence Forfeo pour vos clients.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section id="signup" style="padding: 100px 20px; text-align: center;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 40px;">Initialisez votre Laboratoire</h2>
        <div class="glass-card" style="margin: 0 auto; width: 450px;">
            <form action="/signup-entreprise" method="POST">
                <input type="text" name="nom" placeholder="Nom de votre entreprise" required>
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email de contact" required>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Mot de passe" required>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="background:#fff; color:#000;">Lancer l'inscription</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/forfy') %>

    <script>
        window.addEventListener('load', () => {
            const loader = document.getElementById('loader');
            loader.style.opacity = '0';
            setTimeout(() => loader.style.display = 'none', 500);
        });
        document.querySelectorAll('a, button').forEach(el => {
            el.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                if(el.tagName === 'A' && el.getAttribute('href').startsWith('#')) return;
                const loader = document.getElementById('loader');
                loader.style.display = 'flex';
                loader.style.opacity = '1';
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
